Certiorari Denied. (See also No. 254, Misc., supra.)

No. 376. Gaynor v. Metals Reserve Co. H. C. Harper for petitioner. Solicitor General Perlman, Assistant Attorney General Morison and Paul A. Sweeney filed a brief for the United States opposing the petition.
